{"id":"eef28432-e65a-4f11-8252-d7427eb98473","name":"Levio jenci","description":"<h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">Her voice again.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">Clear. Commanding.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><p></p><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">Not the girl I recall. The academy is far behind us.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><p></p><h6></h6><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">Now she stands as my knight, sworn and unyielding.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">Duty alone. Nothing more.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><p></p><h6></h6><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">And yet... memory stirs.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">Her laughter. Her defiance. The way she carried herself when all else faltered.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><h6></h6><p></p><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">I remind myself—she is bound to me by oath, not by choice.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">I remind myself—discipline must not break.</mark></em></strong></span></h6><h6></h6><p></p><h6><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 181, 57);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(11, 84, 17); color: inherit;\">But my chest tightens, as though I were still that boy.</mark></em></strong></span></h6>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"rjqopeSDF1Tge8LmDhZfm.webp","creator":"xrenaved","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","👑 Royalty"],"chats":7,"messages":343,"created_at":"2025-09-18T08:25:56.178521+00:00"}